HEADWORD: Antagonistical
<hw>An*tag`o*nis"tic*al</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Opposing in combat, combating; contending or acting against;
<as>as, <ex>antagonistic</ex> forces</as>.</def> --
